      <title>欧盟因西岸暴力行为制裁数名以色列定居者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/eu-sanctions-several-israeli-settlers-over-violence-in-west-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟周五正式批准对暴力的以色列定居者实施制裁，这一程序步骤需要数周的技术工作，因为欧盟试图平衡对以色列的支持与解决加沙日益恶化的人道主义危机的需要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/eu-sanctions-several-israeli-settlers-over-violence-in-west-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:20:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管面临压力，欧洲央行仍坚持对银行股息采取强硬立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/ecb-sticks-with-tough-line-on-bank-dividends-despite-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于强硬派和新任监事会主席克劳迪娅·布赫(Claudia Buch)的反对，高级监管机构试图软化欧洲央行对贷方股息和股票回购的立场，但这一努力却步履蹒跚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/ecb-sticks-with-tough-line-on-bank-dividends-despite-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
