      <title>以色列对伊朗空军基地进行有限无人机袭击以回击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/iran-acknowledges-drone-attack-by-israel-and-says-it-failed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，以色列周五早上对伊朗进行了反击，在一次无人机行动中袭击了一个军事地点，但规模有限，似乎造成的损失很小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/iran-acknowledges-drone-attack-by-israel-and-says-it-failed</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 09:47:43 GMT</pubDate>
