    <item>
      <title>以色列争论报道的对伊朗的袭击是否足够大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/israel-debates-if-reported-iran-attack-is-strong-enough-message</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于以色列对周五对伊朗的报复性袭击保持官方沉默，其分析人士和官员对此次袭击的规模是强弱的标志进行了权衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/israel-debates-if-reported-iran-attack-is-strong-enough-message</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 08:43:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里希·苏纳克承诺如果保守党赢得选举将进行福利改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/rishi-sunak-plans-uk-sick-note-review-in-push-to-tackle-inactivity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相苏纳克表示，如果保守党赢得下届大选，他将改革英国的福利制度，并承诺减少因健康原因失业的人数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/rishi-sunak-plans-uk-sick-note-review-in-push-to-tackle-inactivity</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪在印度世界最大的选举中竞选第三个任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/india-elections-day-1-voting-in-world-s-largest-democracy-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近10亿印度人周五开始在持续六周多的选举中投票，权衡是否给予总理纳伦德拉·莫迪第三个五年任期，以继续其经济和印度教民族主义政策的混合政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/india-elections-day-1-voting-in-world-s-largest-democracy-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
